snippet.title: Influence - Populate the Belt Trailer
snippet.description:
Influence is a space strategy MMO where players own the world they create. Colonize asteroids, build infrastructure, fly ships, engage in PVP combat. Expand your influence within the Adalia star system.

Website: https://www.influenceth.io
Wiki: https://wiki.influenceth.io
Twitter: https://twitter.com/influenceth
Discord: https://discord.gg/pEeBHF8WsK

Music composed by Timothy Seals: https://soundcloud.com/timothy-seals
Video Editing & Production by Ryan Dunleavy: https://www.ryandunleavy.com/
